@startuml sd_EmployeeService_search
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title EmployeeService.search(params, pageable) - 多条件分页查询员工

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "EmployeeController" as Ctrl
participant "EmployeeService" as Service
participant "EmployeeRepository" as Repo
participant "Specification" as Spec
participant "Employee\n(实体)" as Entity

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/employees\n?name=张&deptId=1&active=true&page=0&size=10
Ctrl -> Service: search(params, pageable)
Service -> Service: 构造Specification
note right of Service #F0F8FF
  **动态拼接Predicate:**
  1. name: LIKE %keyword%
  2. employeeNo: LIKE %keyword%
  3. departmentId: = equal
  4. active: = equal
  用 cb.and() 组合
end note
Service -> Spec: 创建 (root, query, cb)
activate Spec
Service -> Repo: findAll(spec, pageable)
Repo -> Spec: apply(root, query, cb)
Spec --> Repo: Predicate[]
Repo --> Service: Page<Employee>
deactivate Spec
Service --> Ctrl: Page<Employee>
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<Page>\n(含content/totalPages/totalElements)
@enduml
